<section class="tracki-manual">
  <div class="page-width page-width--smaller">

    <!-- TOP AREA -->
    <div class="tracki-manual__header">

      <h1 class="tracki-manual__title">
        {{ section.settings.title }}
      </h1>

      <div class="tracki-manual__top">

        <!-- PRODUCT IMAGE -->
        <div class="tracki-manual__image">
          {% if section.settings.product_image != blank %}
            <img 
              src="{{ section.settings.product_image | img_url: 'master' }}" 
              alt="{{ section.settings.product_image.alt | escape }}">
          {% endif %}
        </div>

        <!-- SIDE NAVIGATION -->
        <div class="tracki-manual__nav">
          <ul>
            {% for block in section.blocks %}
              <li>
                <a href="{{ block.settings.anchor }}">
                  {{ block.settings.label }}
                </a>
              </li>
            {% endfor %}
          </ul>
        </div>

      </div>
    </div>

  </div>
</section>
{% comment %} <section id="general-info" class="general-info-section">
  <div class="page-width page-width--smaller">
    <!-- CONTENT AREA -->
    <div class="tracki-manual__content divider-sec">
        <h2>General information</h2>
        <p>
            These operating instructions are for the Tracki Pro 4G GPS tracker, which will simply be referred to as ‘tracker’ in the following. They contain important information regarding set-up and operation. Before using the tracker, please read the operating instructions carefully. This particularly applies to the safety notes. Failure to adhere to these operating instructions may result in severe injury or damage to the tracker.
        </p>
        <p>
            The operating instructions are based on the standards and rules in force in the European Union. When abroad, you must also observe country-specific guideless and laws. keep the operating instructions for future use. If you pass the tracker on to third parties, please be absolute sure, to include these operating instructions.
        </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section> {% endcomment %}

{% comment %} <section id="initial_setup" class="initialsetup-section">
  <div class="page-width page-width--smaller">
    <!-- CONTENT AREA -->
    <div class="tracki-manual__content divider-sec">
        <h2>Initial set-up</h2>
        <h6>Installing and charging the battery</h6>
        <p>When you unpack the tracker for the first time, the battery is empty. Charge it as follows:</p>
        <ol>
            <li>Connect the charging plug of the charging cable to the tracker with the Type C.</li>
            <li>Connect the other end of the charging cable to the USB power adaptor and then to the power socket. Alternatively you can also connect the charging cable to a computer.</li>
            <li>Charge the tracker for 6 hours.</li>
            <li>The red light will blink whilst charging. When the tracker is fully charged, the light will turn solid red.</li>
        </ol>
    </div>
    <div class="tracki-manual__content divider-sec">
        <h6>Turning the tracker on</h6>
        <ol>
            <li>Take the tracker outside so that it is in the open air.</li>
            <li>Verify tracker is ON by pressing and hold the ON/OFF button. Red light will blink.</li>
            <li>Place the tracker down and leave it for at least 15 minutes. This allows the tracker to perform its initial GPS positioning, which is required for the device to function correctly.</li>   
        </ol>
        <p>&nbsp;</p>
        <p>Once completed, the tracker will be ready for use and can be activated. <br/><span class="grey-text">Please note: this procedure is only required the very first time the tracker is turned on.</span></p>
    </div>
    <div class="tracki-manual__content divider-sec">
        <h6>Activating the tracker via Web</h6>
        <ol>
            <li>Open your internet browser and go to <a href="#">app.tracki.com</a></li>
            <li>Register and create your Tracki account, then wait for the activation email from Tracki, click on the confirmation link, then login.</li>
            <li>Click on “Add Tracker” and follow the on-screen instructions.</li>
            <li>Insert your tracker IMEI and Device ID, and follow the instructions to activate your service plan.</li>
        </ol>
    </div>
    <div class="tracki-manual__content divider-sec">
        <h6>Activating the tracker via App</h6>
        <ol>
            <li>Download the Tracki app from the Apple Store or Google Play.</li>
            <li>Register or log into your Tracki account.</li>
            <li>Tap on "+" icon to add the device and follow the activation instructions.</li>
        </ol>
    </div>
  </div>
</section> {% endcomment %}

